22-030-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I see you every day, so I notice@these things, you know?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200401,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Thanks, Madoka."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-10"},{"id":200101,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But you don't have to worry anymore."},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm going to defeat Witches."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Like, I do have times where I feel down,@and hate myself..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But if I can hold my head high and say@I'm a hero who keeps this town safe..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm sure I can learn to accept myself@for who I am."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200401,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, I'm okay now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Madoka, I'd be happy if you stuck@around as my witness."},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104205/vo_full_906122-030-17"}],